
<div class="container">
    <div class="hero-section">
        <h2>안녕하세요! 어떤 증상이 있으신가요?</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">간단한 질문으로 맞춤 건강 조언을 받아보세요</p>
    </div>
    
    <form action="/diagnose" method="POST" class="diagnosis-form">
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="age">연세가 어떻게 되시나요?</label>
            <select id="age" name="age" required>
                <option value="">선택해주세요</option>
                <option value="60-65">60-65세</option>
                <option value="66-70">66-70세</option>
                <option value="71-75">71-75세</option>
                <option value="76-80">76-80세</option>
                <option value="80+">80세 이상</option>
            </select>
        </div>
        
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="gender">성별</label>
            <div class="radio-group">
                <label class="radio-label">
                    <input type="radio" name="gender" value="남성" required>
                    <span>남성</span>
                </label>
                <label class="radio-label">
                    <input type="radio" name="gender" value="여성" required>
                    <span>여성</span>
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="symptoms">어떤 증상이 있으신가요?</label>
            <textarea id="symptoms" name="symptoms" placeholder="예: 머리가 아파요, 기침이 나요, 배가 아파요" required></textarea>
        </div>
        
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">진단받기</button>
    </form>
    
    <div class="emergency-section">
        <h3>응급상황인가요?</h3>
        <a href="/emergency" class="btn-emergency">응급전화 안내</a>
    </div>
</div>
